summary 'Puppet module to create virtual machines defined by code via Kickstart files.'
description 'Combining libvirt and Kickstart to create and setup a fresh and up to date virtual machine in just a few minutes.
All the configuration is defined in Puppet without the need for a dedicated server to distribute Kickstart configuration files.'
project_page 'https://github.com/tux-o-matic/puppet-vkick'

